## Tips & Common Mistakes

### üí° Pro Tips

1. **Keep a Prompt Library**: Save prompts that work well for reuse and modification
2. **Experiment with Different AIs**: The same prompt may yield different results across tools
3. **Use Conversation History**: Build on previous responses rather than starting from scratch
4. **Be Polite**: While not necessary, many find that courteous prompts yield better results
5. **Verify Information**: AI can make mistakes‚Äîalways fact-check important information

### ‚ö†Ô∏è Common Pitfalls

1. **Treating AI as a Search Engine**: AI generates responses; it doesn't just retrieve facts
2. **Not Iterating on Prompts**: The first response is rarely perfect‚Äîrefine and improve
3. **Ignoring AI Limitations**: AI can't access real-time data (in most cases) or personal files
4. **Over-Relying on AI**: Use AI to enhance, not replace, your critical thinking
5. **Forgetting Privacy**: Don't share sensitive or confidential information in AI chats

